Being president sure does take a toll. A new animated GIF put together by the team at healthtrends.com, a health news website currently in development, shows President Barack Obama from childhood through today. But of all the years of aging in the GIF, it’s the last eight that seem to hit the hardest... at least on the outside. On the inside, he may actually be getting healthier ― according to his most recent medical report, anyway. Share this slide: